<div class="prose">

<p>Four planets, shown as your eye (or a camera, or something else — that's the point) would see them. No names, no labels, no scale. Work through the three questions below <strong>before</strong> anything gets flipped.</p>

<div class="callout">
  <div class="callout-title">Class rule</div>
  Nothing gets flipped until we finish question 3. If you're revisiting this page after Block 1 — flip away. First-timers: looking first is the whole exercise.
</div>

</div>

<style>
  .pg-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
    margin: 28px 0;
  }
  .pg-card {
    perspective: 1200px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    padding: 0;
    font: inherit;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pg-inner {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    transition: transform 0.6s;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
  }
  .pg-card.flipped .pg-inner { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .pg-inner { transition: none; }
  }
  .pg-face {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .pg-front {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
  }
  .pg-back {
    background: var(--accent-light);
    color: var(--ink);
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .pg-disk {
    width: min(180px, 70%);
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    background: #000;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .pg-letter {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .pg-hint { font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.7; }
  .pg-name { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .pg-origin {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--accent-dark);
  }
  .pg-origin.artist { background: var(--ai-orange); color: var(--ink); }
  .pg-note { font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.45; }
  .pg-credit { font-size: 0.72rem; opacity: 0.75; }
  .pg-controls { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin: 4px 0 8px; }
  .pg-controls button {
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .pg-controls button:hover { background: var(--accent-light); }
</style>

