      <div class="pg-face pg-back">
        <span class="pg-name">Earth</span>
        <span class="pg-origin">PHOTOGRAPH</span>
        <p class="pg-note">A single photograph, taken by a human with a handheld camera — the Apollo 17 crew, December 1972, on the way to the Moon. The "Blue Marble."</p>
        <span class="pg-credit">NASA (AS17-148-22727)</span>
      </div>
